<div>
    <h2>
        Products</h2>
    <p>
        Why does your Small size start with 6 weeks?
        <br />
        We recommend that during the first 6 weeks you swaddle your baby or use a romper
        or sleep suit. However we realize that each baby is unique in its personality and
        in its size. That is why we have placed extra information on sizing in our product
        description. Just make sure that the armholes and the neck opening are not too wide
        for your baby. If you have any sizing questions please do not hesitate to contact
        us at info@hushpuresleep.com
    </p>
    <p>
        Why do you only have sleep sacks available?
        <br />
        We are a start up company. Our first goal is to bring the softest sleep sack ever
        to the United States. But don’t worry other products will follow soon. And of course
        they will have the same distinctive European design and the gorgeous softness.
    </p>
</div>
