</div>
<div>
    <h2>
        Quality and care</h2>
    <p>
        What is the fabric you use?
        <br />
        We use gorgeously soft Pima cotton. It is considered to be one of the superior blends
        of cotton and is extremely durable and absorbent.
    </p>
    <p>
        Are all your fabrics organic?
        <br />
        Yes. We believe that organic fabric is the future. Better for us, better for our
        children and better for the following generations.
    </p>
    <p>
        Why organic cotton?
        <br />
        Organic cotton contains no chemicals that could be harmful for a small developing
        baby. It is pure and better for sensitive skin. Do we need to say more.
    </p>
    <p>
        How should I wash my sleep sack?
        <br />
        Our sleep sack is machine washable. Use the gentle or delicate cycle with lukewarm
        water. We recommend the use of non-phosphate soap. Line dry, or tumble dry at a
        low temperature.
    </p>
</div>
