</div>
<div>
    <h2>
        Sustainable</h2>
    <p>
        Where are your products made?
        <br />
        Our first batch was made in Europe. However our aim is to have the smallest footprint
        possible. Which means that products sold in the United States will be made in the
        USA.
    </p>
    <p>
        Are you a sustainable company?
        <br />
        We try to be. The world we live in today asks us to consider the wellbeing of the
        planet and her people. Unfortunately, quality and sustainability do not yet always
        go hand in hand. At the moment not all our production partners are sustainable.
        Hopefully, as more and more companies become environmentally conscious, we will
        be able to be 100% sustainable in the future.
    </p>
</div>
