<div>
    <h2>
        Shipping and returns</h2>
    <p>
        How is my order shipped?
        <br />
        Within 1-3 working days your order is shipped from our distribution hub in California.
        Upon placing an order you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number
        of your package.
    </p>
    <p>
        What are your shipping fees?
        <br />
        We have no shipping fees. We are happy that you are buying our products.
    </p>
    <p>
        Can the shipping address be different to the credit card billing address?
        <br />
        Yes of course. We want to make shopping with us as easy as possible for you. We
        understand you may want to send our product as a gift. Please tick the box at check
        out that states shipping address is different as billing address.
    </p>
    <p>
        What is your return policy?
        <br />
        Our return fees are zero. Of course we want you to be happy with our product. If
        for any reason you are not, please do let us know and use the return form included
        in your package.
    </p>
    <p>
        How should I return your product?
        <br />
        Included in your package is a return form. Please fill that out and let our shipping
        company pick up your package. We do ask you to only return unused products.
    </p>
    <p>
        Within how many days should I return your product?
        <br />
        We do ask you to return our product within 14 days upon receiving.
    </p>
</div>
